‚Ä¢ Strength Training (2-3 times/week): Focus on compound exercises like squats, lunges, deadlifts, push-ups, and rows. Include core work. This builds muscle, boosts metabolism, and supports performance${userData.sportsInterest ? ` on the field` : ''}.
